text: Hello everyone! I’m a graduate-researcher statistician at the University of Warwick, living in Oxford, UK. I’ve been using R for about seven years, for both my academic research and personal projects. I love both the language and the community around it. It’s been wonderful seeing how both of those have grown over the years and I’m excited to be part of that continued growth.
